Privacy Policy for Pelagos

1. Introduction
Thank you for playing "Pelagos." We respect and value your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines our commitment to safeguarding your personal information and ensuring that you continue to trust us with your data.

2. No Collection of Personal Data
"Pelagos" is designed to be a completely local experience. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data or information while you use the game. All game-related data, such as scores or progress, is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to us or any third parties.

3. Permissions
The game may request certain permissions, such as access to storage, to function correctly. However, these permissions are solely for the operational needs of the game and are not used to collect personal data.

4. Third-Party Integrations
"Pelagos" does not integrate with third-party services that might collect your personal data.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be notified within the game itself or on our official channels.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at "rgarhyan@gmail.com"
